data.description: One Level Living at its finest! This single level all brick home sits nestled in the heart of Blackfoot just a block away from Blackfoot High school and Stoddard Elementary. Step inside to discover a spacious living area flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a functional dream centrally located in the home with lots of counter space and storage. This home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing a comfortable and convenient living space. Built-in storage is a recurring theme throughout the home, ensuring organization is a breeze. The large 2-car garage comes equipped with more built-in storage, offering ample room for your vehicles and belongings. Enjoy the serenity of the outdoors in the fenced backyard, complete with a variety of raised garden beds for those with a green thumb. The property is also equipped with a full sprinkler system, making lawn maintenance a simple task. This home is perfect for those seeking a one-level haven with a blend of convenience, style, and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your new home!
